As of the 2010 census, the borough was 90.1% White, 3.6% Black or African American, 0.5% Native American, 3.3% Asian, and 1.7% were two or more races. 3.6% of the population were of Hispanic or Latino ancestry <ref name="USAToday">{{cite web|title=Census 2010: Pennsylvania|url=https://www.usatoday.com/news/nation/census/profile/PA}}</ref>

